Fluxo de Dados Completo
Usuário vê Landing → clica "Start" → Connect (Phantom) → Experiment
  ↓
  Para cada um dos 4 estímulos:
    observe (35s ou manual) → react-immediate (4 opções) →
    react-association (3 opções) → react-scales (4 sliders 0-10)
  ↓
  submitAll():
    1. computeISS()           → score 0-100 + perfil de apego
    2. generateHash(payload)  → SHA-256 hex
    3. uploadToIPFS(payload)  → ipfs://... URI
    4. buildNftMetadata()     → Metaplex JSON
    5. uploadNftMetadata()    → ipfs://... URI
    6. POST /api/nft/mint     → servidor minta NFT + Memo tx
  ↓
  Dashboard: ISS gauge + perfil + variáveis E/A/T/D/V + links Solscan

Cálculo do ISS (Imprint Sensitivity Score)
score = scaleScore + associationScore + reactionBonus + varianceScore
      = round(E × 5)         [0–50]
      + round(A × 20)        [0–20]
      + instinctiveReactions × 3  [0–12]
      + min(V × 4, 18)       [0–18]
      = total 0–100
Perfis de apego:
  E < 3  AND A < 0.25           → evitativo
  V ≥ 2.5 AND D ≥ 4             → desorganizado
  E ≥ 6.5 OR (A ≥ 0.5 AND T < 10s) → ansioso
  default                       → seguro

